Author: Tao Zhang <tzhang@microsoft.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 17 07:02:50 2026 +0000

    Merged PR 6494044: More GPU Utilization Features

    - Change the Papyrus model prefix from `~` to `z-` so that endpoints without quota or utilization appear at the bottom.
    - Compute the GPU utilization against the safe quota.
